e with little to no comments.<br />Sorry, this has been on my mind - I've been doing a lot of Objective C at work. While we watch Xcode produce huge complicated binaries from this convoluted stuff and a simple game grows in tens of megabytes from big resources, I like to bring up the daily reminder that Super Mario Bros is less than 64KB...</div>

